        Frontend Designing

1)Lazy loading-process of loading components & modules and also improves application load time and perfomance
 [ ng g m products --route products --module app.module ]

 create a component lazy loaded in the products module  
    -all-products [ ng g c products/all-products]
    -cart [ ng g c products/cart]
    -wishlist [ ng g c products/wishlist ]
    -booking [ ng g c products/booking ]

2.Integration
 connecting between backend to frontend using HttpModule

3.Searching for a product - Behaviour subject
       [ ng g p products/pipes/filter ]

